---
title: Scenario 6 — Rapid Order Changes (Collapse Behaviour)
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant Service as Backend Service
    participant Cache as SourceCache
    participant Sub as Throttled Subscription\n(150ms window)
    participant Box as AnimatedListBox
    participant Pipeline as Pipeline

    Note over Service: Service fires rapid order changes\nfaster than animation can keep up

    Service->>Cache: item[2].Order = 1  (t=0ms)
    Service->>Cache: item[0].Order = 3  (t=20ms)
    Service->>Cache: item[1].Order = 2  (t=40ms)
    Service->>Cache: item[3].Order = 0  (t=60ms)
    Service->>Cache: item[2].Order = 4  (t=80ms)

    Note over Sub: Throttle window (150ms) still open\nAll changes buffered

    Service->>Cache: item[0].Order = 1  (t=100ms)

    Note over Sub: Throttle window expires at t=150ms\nOnly the FINAL state is emitted

    Sub-->>Box: CollectionChanged (Move) — final order only

    Box->>Box: ClassifyChange → OrderChange
    Box->>Pipeline: Enqueue OrderChange(finalState)

    alt Pipeline is idle
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: TryProcessNext immediately
        Pipeline->>Box: ProcessSnapshot(OrderChange)
        Box->>Box: FLIP animates from current → final order\nSingle smooth animation
    else Pipeline is busy (transfer playing)
        Note over Pipeline: Queue: [OrderChange(finalState)]
        Note over Pipeline: Waits for current animation

        Note over Service: MORE rapid changes arrive\nduring the wait

        Service->>Cache: item[1].Order = 0  (t=200ms)
        Service->>Cache: item[3].Order = 2  (t=220ms)
        Sub-->>Box: CollectionChanged after 150ms throttle

        Box->>Pipeline: Check queue for existing OrderChange\nFound! Replace with newer state
        Note over Pipeline: Queue: [OrderChange(newerFinalState)]\nOlder state discarded

        Note over Box: Transfer finishes

        Pipeline->>Box: ProcessSnapshot(OrderChange — newest state)
        Box->>Box: FLIP animates to correct final order
        Note over Box: Result: No matter how many intermediate\norder changes arrived, only one\nFLIP animation plays to the true final state
    end
